Use the diamonds data set

Source: R/use-data.R
use_data_diamonds.Rd

This data set comes with the ggplot2 package. It contains the prices and other attributes of almost 54,000 diamonds.

Usage

use_data_diamonds()

Value

Dataset

See also

ggplot2::diamonds

Examples

use_data_diamonds()
